quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  58,14,"Abaffe tewamanya abo abakwanagana n'abantu Katonda beyasunguwalira, abantu abo mu butuufu si ba mu mmwe wadde si ba mu bali (Bebakwanagana nabo) nebatuuka n'okulayira ku bulimba nga ate ddala bamanyi (ekituufu)"
  58,15,"Katonda yabategekera ebibonerezo ebikambwe, anti mazima byonna byebaakolanga bibi"
  58,16,"(Okulayira kwabwe nti basiramu) baakifuula ekyokuwona, olwo nno nebaziyiza abantu okukola emirimu gya Katonda, bagenda kutuukibwako ebibonerezo ebinyomesa"
  58,17,Emaali yaabwe n'abaana baabwe tebigenda kubagasa naakamu mumaaso g'a Katonda. Abo be bantu bo mumuliro ab'okugubeeramu obugenderevu
  58,18,"Olunaku Katonda lwalibazuukiza bonna nebamulayirira nga bwebaabalayirira mmwe ku nsi nga balowooza nti kyebakoze kyakubagasa. Abange, abo nno beebalimba bennyini"
  58,19,Sitaane yabeefunza okutuusa lweyabeerabiza okwogera ku Katonda. Abo nno be bagoberezi ba Sitaane. Mukimanye nti mazima ab'ekibiina kya Sitaane be b'okufafaganirwa
  58,20,Mazima abo abawakanya Katonda n'omubakawe ba mu bantu abanyoomebwa
  58,21,(Katonda) yakakasa dda nti nze Katonda n'ababaka bange tuli baakuwangula anti Katonda wamaanyi. Nnantakubwa ku mukono
  58,22,"Tewali bantu bonna abakkiriza Katonda n'olunaku lw’enkomerero baalibadde batiitiibya abo abawakanya Katonda n'omubakawe, kababe ba kitaabwe, oba baana baabwe, oba baganda baabwe, oba nga baaluganda lwabwe olwokumpi. Abo nno (abatakola ekyo) Katonda yatebenkeza obukkiriza mu mitima gyabwe, naabawagira naamanyi agava gyali era nga agenda kubayingiza e jjana egikulukutira wansi waazo emigga, nga bakubeera mu zo olubeerera. Katonda yabasiima nga nabo bwebaamusiima. Kisaana kimanyike nti mazima abo b'ebantu ba Katonda abokwesiimira ddala"